headline: Trump plans to endorse JD Vance in contentious Ohio Senate GOP primary: Report
author: Kate Scanlon
sentences: During his campaign, Vance touted an endorsement from Rep. Marjorie Taylor Greene of Georgia, a close ally of Trump who joined Vance on the campaign trail, in what was seen as a move to persuade Trump to back his candidacy.
Vance is also underperforming expectations for his candidacy in recent polling, trailing rivals Josh Mandel, a former state treasurer, and businessman Mike Gibbons.
Vance, like all the candidates in the field, has openly courted Trumps endorsement as a means of differentiating himself from the rest of the field.
NBC News reported that Trump has expressed concern about Vance, citing the Hillbilly Elegy authors criticisms of him as a candidate in 2016.
Vances polling presented a major worry for Trump who doesn't want to waste his endorsement,? the report said.
NBC News reported that Trump is planning to endorse Vance, citing three sources with knowledge.
